{"title":"我爱车间","authors":["晓萍"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱车间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京人民印刷厂　晓萍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骏马，爱草原；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白鸽，爱蓝天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士，爱武器；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人，爱车间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱车间："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记参加劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主任跟班生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导和工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲密无间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党和群众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血肉相连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱车间："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间是革命的熔炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间是革命的摇篮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经得起千锤百炼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶得住风雪严寒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海燕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢与狂风暴雨搏斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕那险峻的万岭千山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱车间："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比先进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠找差距；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学先进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲冲天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮后进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级感情千斤重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超先进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀登高峰永不自满。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱车间："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班班组组递战表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对手对口赛得欢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动竞赛春潮涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比学赶帮浪滔天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马达轰鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机轮飞转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲曲凯歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动人心弦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革新红花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争芳斗艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硕果累累，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光闪闪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硕果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把车间打扮得多么美丽、庄严。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱车间：为人民——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇往直前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠心赤胆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难——战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利——向前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是：我们的壮语、豪言！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}